  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示团队在协作工具之间的典型流转路径。起点是Wiki页面，成员在那里查阅文档后，通常会跳转到看板查看任务状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Wiki到看板是第一个流转。那看完看板之后，成员一般会去哪里？是回到Wiki，还是去其他工具？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "看板之后，如果任务需要讨论，他们会进入聊天室进行实时沟通。这是一个常见的协作模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把聊天室接在看板后面了。接下来聊天室讨论完之后，流程往哪里走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "讨论中如果发现具体问题，需要记录和跟踪，这时候会转到问题追踪器。聊天室到IssueTracker是第三个环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "IssueTracker已连接。这里有个细节想确认：IssueTracker之后，团队是回到聊天室继续讨论，还是去其他工具？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "会回到另一个聊天室，可能是专门的Bug讨论频道。注意这里不是之前的那个聊天室，是第二个ChatRoom节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我标记为第二个聊天室节点。那Bug讨论完之后，流程怎么继续？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "讨论完需要更新文档，所以回到Wiki页面，把解决方案写进去。这是第五个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Wiki页面更新后，成员会再次去看板更新任务状态吗？还是直接去别的地方？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，回到看板把任务拖到完成列。这是第六个节点，第二个看板。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "第二个看板已添加。目前我们有Wiki→看板→聊天室→IssueTracker→聊天室→Wiki→看板，共七个节点。还需要继续延伸吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。实际上团队有多个项目看板，完成一个任务后可能要去另一个项目的看板继续工作。所以再加一个看板节点，第三个看板。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "第三个看板已连接。这个跨项目跳转之后呢？流程怎么收尾？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "跨项目工作后，需要查阅另一个项目的Wiki文档，所以连接到第二个Wiki页面。这是第八个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "第二个Wiki页面之后，流程要闭环回到最开始的Wiki页面吗？还是就这样结束？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要闭环。最后从第二个Wiki页面连回第一个Wiki页面，形成循环。这样表示团队协作是一个持续迭代的过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "循环已建立。我梳理一下当前结构：起点WikiA→看板B→聊天室C→IssueTrackerD→聊天室E→WikiF→看板G→看板H→WikiI→回到WikiA。总共九个节点形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但让我再检查一下。IssueTracker之后是第二个聊天室，这个没问题。但WikiF到看板G，再到看板H，这两个看板是连续跳转，中间不需要其他步骤吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我确认一下，您说的是WikiF→看板G→看板H这个链条。目前图上是直接相连的，没有其他节点。如果不需要中间步骤，这样画是正确的。需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不需要调整，直接相连是对的，表示快速切换项目看板的场景。整个流程图就这样定稿了，九个节点形成完整的协作循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
